Package fi.explorator

Provides classes for path finding algorithms and necessary classes to represent 2D Grid.

          Description

Class Summary
Cell Represents single cell in 2D grid.
Edge Edge between 2 Cell objects.
FloydWarshall Floyd-Warshall implementation.
Grid 2D grid which represents the area where the starting point and ending point of the path resides.
Path Path class which keeps list of Cell objects which forms the path.
PathFinder Abstract base class which all path finding algorithms will be extending from.
 

Enum Summary
PathFinderType Algorithm type enumaration.
 

Package fi.explorator Description

Provides classes for path finding algorithms and necessary classes to represent 2D Grid.

Supporting following algorithms: Floyd-Warshall, Dijkstra and A*
